OL,5,CSURVIVING A VEGETARIAN CHRISTMAS! R+o' 
OL,7, "Christmas just would not be Christmas 
OL,8, withoutCturkey.GIt must be hard for    
OL,9, you. What will you be having then?     
OL,11, "Go on, it's Christmas.COnce a year    
OL,12,Cwon't make a difference!'GIf you're a  
OL,13, vegetarian, undoubtably you've heard   
OL,14, all these comments before," says Chris 
OL,15, Dessent from The Vegetarian Society.   
OL,17, "ButCdon't panic,GChristmas needn't be 
OL,18, a headache - there are loads of things 
OL,19, you can do to make it go with a bang!" 
