OL,5,CSURVIVING A VEGETARIAN CHRISTMAS! R+o' 
OL,7, "If turkey's not your thing,Cgo nuts," 
OL,8, advises expert Chris Dessent. "Look out
OL,9, for vegetarian recipes such as Pine Nut
OL,10, Risotto, Chestnut Bourguignonne Pie or 
OL,11, the vegetarian classic, nut roast.     
OL,13, "Nuts areChighly nutritiousGand can    
OL,14, provide you with calcium, zinc and     
OL,15, essential fatty acids.                 
OL,17, "Why not experiment withCseasonal      
OL,18,Cwinter vegGlike swede and parsnips?    
OL,19, Roast, team, boil, fry or bake them!"  
