OL,5,CSURVIVING A VEGETARIAN CHRISTMAS! R+o' 
OL,7, "Christmas is the time to stock your   
OL,8, cupboards full of theCjuices of the    
OL,9,Cvine,"Gsays Chris Dessent from The     
OL,10, Vegetarian Society.                    
OL,12, "Vegetarian wine is free from finings  
OL,13, such as gelatine and isinglass - the   
OL,14,Cbladder of tropical fishG- often used  
OL,15, to clarify wine.                       
OL,17, "Look out for The Vegetarian Society's 
OL,18,C'V' symbol,Gguaranteeing a product is  
OL,19, 100% vegetarian."                      
