OL,5,CSURVIVING A VEGETARIAN CHRISTMAS! R+o' 
OL,7, "If you've over indulged, you don't    
OL,8, needCa bacon buttieGto sort your hang- 
OL,9, over out" says expert Chris Dessent.   
OL,11, "The best veggie hangover cure is a    
OL,12,Cbanana milkshake,Gmade from soya milk, 
OL,13, honey and ground almonds and of course,
OL,14, bananas. Throw them together and whisk!
OL,16, "In addition, you can still eat mince  
OL,17, pies at Christmas, just make sure you  
OL,18, get the vegetarian suet variety.       
OL,19,CTraditional suet uses animal fat."     
