OL,5,CSURVIVING A VEGETARIAN CHRISTMAS! R+o' 
OL,7, "Try explaining to concerned family    
OL,8, members and friends that a vegetarian  
OL,9, diet isCperfectly healthy,"Gsays Chris 
OL,10, Dessent of The Vegetarian Society.     
OL,12, "Wherever you go there will always be  
OL,13, some joker who thinksCveggies are nuts.
OL,15, "If one of these types corners you over
OL,16, the yule log and starts to make turkey 
OL,17, noises or asking pointless questions   
OL,18, about whether carrots feel pain, just  
OL,19,Claugh at them, they're a lost cause."  
