OL,4,B``````````````````````````````````R.{w!
OL,5,CPORT & STILTON PATE               R+o' 
OL,6,R$G2oz/50g butter or vegetarian marge   
OL,7,R$G1 bunch spring onions, chopped       
OL,8,R$G2floz/60ml crusted port              
OL,9,R$Gzest of half a lemon                 
OL,10,R$G4oz/110g vegetarian stilton, crumbled
OL,11,R$G1 small bunch parsley, chopped       
OL,12,CMETHOD:                                
OL,13,BGMelt the butter in a saucepan and    
OL,14,   sweat the onions - remove from heat. 
OL,15,BGWhen cool add the port and simmer for
OL,16,   3 mins before adding the remaining   
OL,17,   ingredients. Stir in well.           
OL,18,BGTransfer to a blender, divide into   
OL,19,   ramekins and chill for two hours.    
OL,20,B``````````````````````````````````6/11`
