OL,5,CCHESTNUT BOURGUIGNONNE PIE         R+o'
OL,6,R$G4oz/10g dried chestnuts, soaked for  
OL,7,   6-8 hours                            
OL,8,R$G2 bay leaves                         
OL,9,R$G1 sprig fresh rosemary               
OL,10,R$G7floz/210ml vegetarian red wine      
OL,11,R$G10floz/300ml vegetable stock or water
OL,12,R$G1oz/25g butter or soya margarine     
OL,13,R$G8 small shallots, peeled             
OL,14,R$G4oz/110g chestnut mushrooms, wiped   
OL,15,R$G2oz/50g button mushrooms, wiped      
OL,16,R$G2tsp/10ml dijon mustard              
OL,17,R$G2-3tbsp/30-45ml tamari or soy sauce  
OL,18,R$Gfresh parsley, chopped               
OL,19,R$G8oz/225g puff pastry      CMethod >>>
OL,20,B``````````````````````````````````7/11`
