OL,1,R/epp`pp`p pp0pp0pz5`p`pb1pp0`0Q 20 
OL,2,R/j7j7j7 s{5k5k5j7j7j5k5n1R x0 
OL,3,R j}j}j} ~5j5~5j}j5j5j5j5R+?!
OL,4,B``````````````````````````````````R.{w!
OL,5,CCHESTNUT BOURGUIGNONNE PIE        R+o' 
OL,6,CMETHOD:                                
OL,7,BGPreheat the oven to 200C/400F/Gas    
OL,8,   Mark 6. Place the soaked chestnuts,  
OL,9,   herbs and 5floz of wine in a saucepan
OL,10,   with vegetable stock to cover and    
OL,11,   cook until tender.                   
OL,13,BGDrain the chestnuts, reserving the   
OL,14,   liquid. Melt the butter in a frying  
OL,15,   pan and saute the onions until brown.
OL,17,BGAdd the mushrooms and cook for a     
OL,18,   further 4 - 5 mins.                  
OL,19,                            C  Contd >>>
OL,20,B``````````````````````````````````8/11`
