OL,1,R/epp`pp`p pp0pp0pz5`p`pb1pp0`0Q 20 
OL,2,R/j7j7j7 s{5k5k5j7j7j5k5n1R x0 
OL,3,R j}j}j} ~5j5~5j}j5j5j5j5R+?!
OL,4,B``````````````````````````````````R.{w!
OL,5,CCHESTNUT BOURGUIGNONNE PIE        R+o' 
OL,6,CMETHOD:                                
OL,7,BGAdd the chestnuts, the remaining red 
OL,8,   wine and sufficient chestnut cooking 
OL,9,   liquor to cover.                     
OL,10,BGBring to the boil and simmer for 20 -
OL,11,   30 minutes. Stir in the mustard,     
OL,12,   tamari and cook for a further 5 mins.
OL,14,BGCheck seasoning and consistency and  
OL,15,   adjust as necessary.                 
OL,16,BGSpoon the mixture into a pie dish.   
OL,17,   Roll out the pastry on a floured     
OL,18,   surface and place on top of filling. 
OL,19,BGBake for about 20 mins until golden. 
