OL,4,B``````````````````````````````````R.{w!
OL,5,CROAST POTATOES & PARSNIPS WITH    R+o' 
OL,6,CONIONS, HERBS & CHERRY TOMATOES        
OL,7,R$G6 medium potatoes, peeled and halved 
OL,8,R$G4 parsnips, peeled and sliced        
OL,9,R$Gdried mixed herbs                    
OL,10,R$G2 onions, cut into thin rings        
OL,11,R$G60-90ml/4-6tbsp sunflower oil        
OL,12,R$G225g/8oz cherry tomatoes             
OL,13,CMETHOD:                                
OL,14,BGPre-heat the oven to 200C/400F/Gas   
OL,15,   Mark 6. Parboil the potatoes and     
OL,16,   place in a roasting tin with the     
OL,17,   parsnips, onions and herbs.          
OL,18,BGDrizzle with oil and roast for 40    
OL,19,   mins. Add the tomatoes and serve!    
